Fix error on windows.
Fix recent regressions on Windows.
Add +authcheck view for nginx auth_request module.
Replicas always need to be able to download packages.

Prepare release.

Handle empty doczip.

The hash file is now stored outside the unpack directory and used as the lock file.
Use lockfile for remove_docs.
Mention devpi-gen-secret when secret is missing.

Only retry tox with no tests for environment creation, don't retry actual test runs.

Allow nightly tests of devpi-server to fail.

Register replicas devpiserver_auth_user hook with tryfirst.

This prevents other plugins from trying to authenticate the +replica user.
Don't mark wheels as universal since we don't support Python 2 anymore.
Use a lock file to prevent concurrent unpacking of documentation.
